{"tid":578163,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］俾痴線親戚發錢惡點解決？","createTime":"2018-03-02T11:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T12:19:02.000Z","uid":146869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ee3585da3cda6cd249a5680ce166148e4a1d93","tid":578163,"uid":146869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"有個精神病既親戚呢排踩過上門幾次同屋企人嘈<br />\n自己爛賭輸撚哂啲錢 以前都成日問我地借錢 從來都係有借無錢<br />\n依排仲走上屋企嘈 話大陸間屋佢有份 要將每個月收既租分啲俾佢（我老豆同佢係兩兄弟，上一輩留低間屋俾佢地，但佢從來無番過去 又唔理間屋既野）<br />\n我住緊hall都係呢排番屋企先知件事<br />\n今日咁岩俾我睇住佢連續打10幾個電話來轟炸<br />\n本身諗住唔理佢由佢慢慢打 最後一聽電話 條賤種發撚哂癲狂屌 又恐嚇我屋企人話斬撚死佢地<br />\n個親戚有精神病 一直都神撚化化咁 又唔可以屌佢激佢 癲起上嚟唔知會做咩<br />\n俾呢啲親戚睇中左要點做先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/192006_70f6f527ad8c0eed9cdcd5a9b9aaa613.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F192006_70f6f527ad8c0eed9cdcd5a9b9aaa613.png&h=ee319e27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/192007_917dae5f9b2c3e254a01b9995cc73034.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F192007_917dae5f9b2c3e254a01b9995cc73034.png&h=94593cb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c1dd345e12ff62283eaa33292870b4aa82216f8","tid":578163,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"報警"},{"pid":"43b95da52326cef783b908a02133cc2ec581f53e","tid":578163,"uid":46277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"報警啦"},{"pid":"146deab0327f9d15a0bf4d1d52c6ffa6659b1ea8","tid":578163,"uid":146869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"43b95da52326cef783b908a02133cc2ec581f53e","tid":578163,"uid":46277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"報警啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:30:52.000Z","msg":"